headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Keysight Technologies (KEYS) After Its Recent 26.6% Share Price Rise?
summary: If you are wondering whether Keysight Technologies is still good value at around US$223 per share, you are not alone. This article is built to help you frame that question clearly. Over the last year the stock has returned 26.6%, with 4.2% over the past 7 days and 8.1% over the last month and year to date, which may have shifted how some investors see its potential and risk.
